OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNHS staff to get paid leave
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter miscarriages         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, NHS England has said any of its staff  
OL,6, who miscarry in the first 24 weeks of  
OL,7, pregnancy can take 10 days' paid leave.
OL,9,FPartners can take five days. And staff 
OL,10,Fwho miscarry after six months will     
OL,11,Fstill be offered paid maternity leave. 
OL,13,FThe policy, adopted by Humber Teaching 
OL,14,FNHS Foundation Trust last year, is now 
OL,15,Fbeing rolled out nationally.           
OL,17,FAn official for the NHS in Wales said  
OL,18,Fit would consider offering a similar   
OL,19,Fscheme. BBC News has also contacted NHS
OL,20,FScotland and Northern Ireland.         
